<p>The Freedom 90 superstar completed her ensemble dark blue hip-hugging flared jeans, and open-toed nude sandals. </p>

<p>On her shoulder Cindy carried a large tan suede purse.</p>

<p>Crawford accessorized with the faintest touches of jewelry, including a silver chain and bracelet.   </p>

