<p>The sighting comes days after the supermodel was seen with her family enjoying a Mexican getaway. </p>

<p>The sidewalk is her runway: Crawford accessorized with the faintest touches of jewelry, including a silver chain and bracelet</p>

<p>Cindy, along with husband Rande Gerber, is parent to young model Kaia Gerber, 19.</p>

<p>The clan was seen with Kaia and her new flame, Euphoria actor Jacob Elordi, living it up in an upscale Los Cabos resort earlier this week.  </p>

<p>Cindy and Rande, 58, soaked up the sun alongside their daughter, whose latest relationship comes after previous romances with the likes of Pete Davidson and Wellington Grant. </p>

